'''Magnopium ferrocongregate''' was a material used in the assembly of [[core bomb]]s.

[[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] ordered a helmsman aboard the ''[[Aurorient Express]]'' to set the ship's [[vapor sampler]]s to search for both [[magnopium]] [[ferrocongregate]] and [[Accellerite/Legends|accellerite]], in order to locate a core bomb planted onboard.

